<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Sage Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A vibrant family-friendly neighborhood in North West Calgary, Sage Hill is one among the five popular communities developed within the Symons Valley Area. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Nestled within the breathtaking slopes of the Symons Valley, the community in Sage Hill enjoys a central location with respect to both the urbane appeal of the city and the quaint charm of the countryside. </p>
